edu.stanford.nlp.stats
Interface CounterInterface<E>

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractCounter, Counter, IntCounter, OpenAddressCounter
public interface CounterInterface<E>

Basic Object to double map. Utility functions are contained in Counters. Class previously known as Counter has been renamed ot Counter and many of its functions deprecated in preference to those in Counters. The prefered Counter implementation is OpenAddressCounter.

Author:
dramage, cer
